  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Consortium project between CA, CASA and ADRA.
Targeting 2,200 households (illegal settlers, physically cut-off after the floods, traditionally marginalized and excluded)
multi purpose cash programming, WASH, emergency shelter and NFI distributions.
Advocacy activities towards compensation and social safety nets initiatives, gender and protection.
NB: activities and target numbers for the entire consortium project</narrative>
